item.description:
Join me for some fun tossing discs at baskets in the woods. You will get some excersize and just have a good ole time. We will meet at Hillside store across from the park to pick up our discs. Bring water, good shoes, long pants, bug spray and dress in layers. Come out and have some fun. There is also no charge.

 We can grab a bite to eat there after if anyone is interested.

http://www.dgcoursereview.com/reviews.php?id=1588&mode=rev

Cindy 603-315-0275
